yuan left in his Alipay account.

00:05:44.479 --> 00:05:46.320
Was that why you were in a hurry

00:05:46.320 --> 00:05:47.760
to do a house ownership transfer?

00:05:48.760 --> 00:05:49.320
Indeed.

00:05:49.320 --> 00:05:50.599
Why didn't you tell us in advance?

00:05:50.599 --> 00:05:51.760
How could I?

00:05:52.239 --> 00:05:53.799
I wasn't sure about it either back then.

00:05:58.719 --> 00:06:00.359
Mingzhu, I realize

00:06:01.960 --> 00:06:03.039
that you're pretty crafty.

00:06:07.580 --> 00:06:08.960
Let's go once you're done packing.

00:06:09.359 --> 00:06:10.760
Mom is still home alone.

00:06:23.479 --> 00:06:24.399
What is this?

00:06:30.599 --> 00:06:31.520
Oh yeah.

00:06:32.440 --> 00:06:34.919
This is the gold lock
I prepared for your baby.

00:06:35.370 --> 00:06:36.640
Why don't you take it with you?

00:06:36.640 --> 00:06:38.599
This is the gold lock
Dad had bought for my baby.

00:06:39.060 --> 00:06:41.850
He wanted to help my child put it on
during his one-month celebration.

00:06:42.070 --> 00:06:43.479
Let me keep it on my child's behalf.

00:06:51.479 --> 00:06:52.320
What is this, then?

00:06:53.380 --> 00:06:56.560
These are the gifts my sister told me to
deliver to him when she needed a favor.

00:06:56.919 --> 00:06:58.479
I have to return them to her.

00:07:03.520 --> 00:07:06.310
Since Dad is no longer around,
you can take anything you like with you.

00:07:10.359 --> 00:07:10.919
Hello?

00:07:11.919 --> 00:07:12.760
My dear classmate.

00:07:15.680 --> 00:07:16.560
Can you hear me?

00:07:17.120 --> 00:07:20.279
I remember that your second uncle
was pretty resourceful.

00:07:20.279 --> 00:07:21.919
He knows everyone.

00:07:24.239 --> 00:07:24.880
He retired?

00:07:26.320 --> 00:07:27.680
How long has he been retired?

00:07:29.719 --> 00:07:31.919
Five years? That's pretty recent.

00:07:32.320 --> 00:07:33.320
He still has authority.

00:07:33.760 --> 00:07:35.479
Can you help me ask him whether...

00:07:40.080 --> 00:07:41.279
I understand.

00:07:42.880 --> 00:07:43.440
Alright.

00:07:44.279 --> 00:07:44.839
Okay.

00:07:45.960 --> 00:07:47.760
Let's keep in touch, then.

00:07:48.200 --> 00:07:48.760
Goodbye.

00:08:05.200 --> 00:08:06.520
I'm pregnant.

00:08:07.060 --> 00:08:08.359
I'm trying to find help for you,

00:08:08.359 --> 00:08:09.580
yet you're playing
video games on the sofa.

00:08:09.599 --> 00:08:11.560
Zhang Hao, it seems
you have a lot of free time.

00:08:12.599 --> 00:08:14.680
You see, I was busy the entire day.

00:08:14.680 --> 00:08:15.860
I'm just trying to relax here.

00:08:16.760 --> 00:08:18.380
You took the words
right out of my mouth.

00:08:21.479 --> 00:08:23.039
Dear, this is what I think.

00:08:23.039 --> 00:08:23.680
You see,

00:08:24.039 --> 00:08:25.839
