if I become a HOD or not.

00:08:26.599 --> 00:08:28.320
The most important thing is to live on.

00:08:29.799 --> 00:08:31.159
Just look at Mingzhu's husband.

00:08:31.880 --> 00:08:34.359
He was good-looking,
and he came from a wealthy family.

00:08:34.359 --> 00:08:36.280
But he passed away at such a young age.

00:08:37.280 --> 00:08:38.560
Look at Mingzhu's father-in-law.

00:08:38.680 --> 00:08:40.280
He was the most
resourceful person we know.

00:08:40.280 --> 00:08:41.800
He lived in a villa,
and drove a sports car.

00:08:41.800 --> 00:08:43.260
Even so, he passed away not long ago.

00:08:43.479 --> 00:08:44.119
Don't you agree?

00:08:51.060 --> 00:08:51.920
You do have a point.

00:08:52.920 --> 00:08:54.280
We have to learn from this lesson.

00:08:57.920 --> 00:08:59.599
Therefore, I need to find

00:08:59.920 --> 00:09:02.400
a tall and handsome hunk

00:09:02.400 --> 00:09:04.519
and have
a passionate relationship with him.

00:09:04.519 --> 00:09:05.920
Who knows when I might die?

00:09:13.960 --> 00:09:14.759
Where are you going?

00:09:15.080 --> 00:09:16.240
To find your ideal partner.

00:09:16.280 --> 00:09:16.920
Go and cook.

00:09:38.400 --> 00:09:40.519
She's only bent on
taking advantage of the situation.

00:09:41.719 --> 00:09:42.400
Look.

00:09:43.280 --> 00:09:45.320
These are all the things
she took from Dad's office.

00:09:48.719 --> 00:09:49.320
Mom.

00:09:50.280 --> 00:09:53.359
The cigarettes and liquor
were delivered by Zhixia to Dad

00:09:53.360 --> 00:09:54.950
when she wanted to ask him for a favor.

00:09:55.170 --> 00:09:57.440
But they weren't delivered,
and the matter wasn't settled.

00:09:58.479 --> 00:10:00.479
Shouldn't we return them to her?

00:10:04.250 --> 00:10:05.359
And, as for this gold lock,

00:10:06.359 --> 00:10:07.839
Dad wanted to keep it for my child.

00:10:08.280 --> 00:10:09.359
You guys can have it first.

00:10:15.080 --> 00:10:16.839
We found this in Dad's safe.

00:10:17.400 --> 00:10:18.239
Take a look.

00:10:21.239 --> 00:10:22.760
I think Dad prepared this audit report

00:10:23.719 --> 00:10:25.960
before everything went to hell.

00:10:27.560 --> 00:10:28.719
His goal was to separate

00:10:28.719 --> 00:10:30.639
