00:12:02.999 --> 00:12:04.560
exactly how much money he owes.

00:12:05.519 --> 00:12:06.320
Tell me after that.

00:12:32.119 --> 00:12:32.960
Mom.

00:12:34.519 --> 00:12:38.160
Mingzhu is in trouble again.

00:12:39.119 --> 00:12:42.800
Please bless her from above.

00:12:44.239 --> 00:12:46.680
No matter if she recognizes me
as her mom or not,

00:12:47.200 --> 00:12:48.920
I hope that my second daughter

00:12:49.400 --> 00:12:52.479
can lead a safe and smooth-sailing life.

00:13:04.460 --> 00:13:05.320
Zhixia, you're here.

00:13:06.240 --> 00:13:07.879
Dale sent us
another batch of foundation

00:13:07.879 --> 00:13:09.080
for us to help promote.

00:13:10.680 --> 00:13:13.440
Looks like they cashed in
on the lipstick boom last time.

00:13:14.040 --> 00:13:15.160
How is it?

00:13:15.160 --> 00:13:15.960
Take a look.

00:13:20.410 --> 00:13:22.160
It's pretty smooth.
It goes on effortlessly.

00:13:22.400 --> 00:13:23.200
Let me help you.

00:13:26.800 --> 00:13:27.479
