00:13:37.519 --> 00:13:38.800
Why are you being so generous?

00:13:38.980 --> 00:13:41.320
The suppliers sent them to us.
It's not like you're spending my money.

00:13:41.320 --> 00:13:42.560
Take it as an employee benefit.

00:13:42.650 --> 00:13:44.920
Don't demand a raise from me
at the end of the year, okay?

00:13:46.320 --> 00:13:48.560
Now, all industries
are super competitive.

00:13:48.960 --> 00:13:51.200
Don't envy other people.

00:13:51.479 --> 00:13:52.999
