to listen to your lecture.

00:13:59.599 --> 00:14:01.320
I'm not giving you a lecture here.

00:14:02.040 --> 00:14:03.960
I'm explaining
the market conditions to you.

00:14:06.119 --> 00:14:08.239
You see, my husband
is running for a position.

00:14:08.260 --> 00:14:09.920
It's just for the position
of a lowly HOD.

00:14:09.920 --> 00:14:11.400
Even so, everyone's
fighting tooth and nail for it.

00:14:11.400 --> 00:14:12.960
It's terrible.

00:14:19.560 --> 00:14:20.239
Maodou.

00:14:20.960 --> 00:14:22.160
Is any of your relatives

00:14:22.160 --> 00:14:24.280
working in the Personnel Bureau?

00:14:24.290 --> 00:14:26.580
Can you tell them to give a shout-out
to Dianlan Group for us?

00:14:26.599 --> 00:14:27.239
Zhixia.

00:14:28.719 --> 00:14:32.479
Why did you think I'd be working here
if any of my relatives

00:14:32.479 --> 00:14:33.879
was working in the Personnel Bureau?

00:14:35.960 --> 00:14:39.200
Therefore, for common folks like us,

00:14:40.479 --> 00:14:42.280
it's better for us to work diligently

00:14:42.280 --> 00:14:44.800
instead of daydreaming about
getting rich quickly.

00:14:45.550 --> 00:14:46.400
Let's make some money!

00:14:46.560 --> 00:14:47.599
How?

00:14:49.719 --> 00:14:51.479
I plan to start a video channel.

00:14:54.080 --> 00:14:56.200
Although your articles aren't great,

00:14:56.200 --> 00:14:58.400
you're quite likable.

00:14:58.400 --> 00:14:59.719
And, you're eloquent as well.

00:15:00.380 --> 00:15:02.160
Why don't you
be in charge of this project?

00:15:02.359 --> 00:15:02.920
Zhixia.

00:15:04.160 --> 00:15:05.150
