Do you know how many days it has been?

00:29:16.759 --> 00:29:17.680
Misters and madams.

00:29:17.799 --> 00:29:19.400
It's truly difficult to meet you guys.

00:29:19.440 --> 00:29:20.279
Yeah, Feng.

00:29:20.279 --> 00:29:21.510
We've been waiting for so long.

00:29:21.520 --> 00:29:22.680
You should give us an account.

00:29:23.660 --> 00:29:24.760
You didn't answer our calls!

00:29:25.110 --> 00:29:27.319
We won't show you mercy
if we don't resolve this today!

00:29:27.319 --> 00:29:29.279
I won't let you off
until you give us an account!

00:29:29.799 --> 00:29:30.920
Listen to us first.

00:29:30.999 --> 00:29:32.239
Listen to us first.

00:29:33.360 --> 00:29:34.120
Misters and madams,

00:29:36.079 --> 00:29:37.039
I know

00:29:38.600 --> 00:29:39.400
some of you.

00:29:40.920 --> 00:29:42.319
And, I don't know some of you.

00:29:42.920 --> 00:29:43.559
But you guys

00:29:43.559 --> 00:29:45.759
were my dad's friends
for several decades.

00:29:46.460 --> 00:29:48.200
You guys even
watched over me and my brother

00:29:48.200 --> 00:29:49.479
as we grew up.

00:29:51.960 --> 00:29:54.680
It's really painful for us
to meet like this today.

00:29:56.719 --> 00:29:58.239
I'm so sorry.

00:29:58.719 --> 00:30:00.479
It's pointless to apologize.

00:30:00.680 --> 00:30:01.759
Don't start that with me!

00:30:01.759 --> 00:30:02.479
We have no choice either.

00:30:02.479 --> 00:30:03.319
Now,

00:30:03.719 --> 00:30:06.200
I'll give you all the straight facts.

00:30:07.519 --> 00:30:08.319
This file contains

00:30:08.880 --> 00:30:11.079
all the funds
in our company's accounts and

00:30:11.079 --> 00:30:12.519
the list of fixed assets.

00:30:13.799 --> 00:30:15.519
The company is now insolvent.

00:30:15.519 --> 00:30:17.440
- What?
- It's insolvent?

00:30:17.440 --> 00:30:18.200
What do you mean?

00:30:18.200 --> 00:30:19.519
What do you mean?
Are you trying to play dirty here?

00:30:19.519 --> 00:30:21.200
A huge factory like this
is actually insolvent?

00:30:21.200 --> 00:30:22.239
Did you guys tamper with the accounts?

00:30:22.239 --> 00:30:23.400
Don't try to trick us!

00:30:23.479 --> 00:30:24.799
Is there no cash in the safe?

00:30:25.279 --> 00:30:27.039
All factories have an emergency fund!

00:30:27.039 --> 00:30:28.319
That's right!

00:30:28.319 --> 00:30:29.400
And, your dad's funeral

00:30:29.400 --> 00:30:31.039
was even held at Lijun Hotel.

00:30:31.039 --> 00:30:32.460
Now that we're asking you for money,

00:30:32.470 --> 00:30:33.600
you're saying that it's insolvent?

00:30:33.600 --> 00:30:34.840
What kind of tricks
are you guys trying to pull here?

00:30:34.840 --> 00:30:36.319
Back then, we put up real money

00:30:36.319 --> 00:30:37.519
to cover Feng's expenses.

00:30:37.560 --> 00:30:39.400
He was able to drive a sports car
and live in a villa.

00:30:39.400 --> 00:30:41.390
And, he even sent you
to England for your studies.

00:30:41.400 --> 00:30:42.600
Now, Feng is gone.

00:30:42.600 --> 00:30:44.160
On account of our ties, we waited until

00:30:44.160 --> 00:30:45.960
after the seventh day of his passing
before we would bring it up.

00:30:45.960 --> 00:30:47.519
But now? You guys...

00:30:47.519 --> 00:30:49.479
You guys have no respect for us at all!

00:30:49.479 --> 00:30:51.120
Yeah. You're just trying to...

00:30:51.120 --> 00:30:52.260
Now, you're doing this to me?

00:30:52.270 --> 00:30:53.200
- What do you mean by that?
- In my opinion,

00:30:53.200 --> 00:30:55.239
you guys are just buying time here.

00:30:55.519 --> 00:30:56.400
For what purpose?

00:30:56.400 --> 00:30:58.320
For them to transfer
all of his assets to them!

00:30:58.519 --> 00:30:59.239
You have a point!

00:30:59.440 --> 00:31:00.039
Look!

00:31:00.039 --> 00:31:00.660
That's not true.

00:31:00.999 --> 00:31:02.680
Misters and madam,

00:31:02.920 --> 00:31:05.039
please listen to us first, okay?

00:31:05.759 --> 00:31:06.239
Fine.

00:31:06.239 --> 00:31:07.360
Go ahead.

00:31:07.370 --> 00:31:10.239
I've always been thankful to you guys
for trusting my father-in-law,

00:31:10.540 --> 00:31:12.719
working together with him,
and covering his expenses.

00:31:13.440 --> 00:31:15.640
But now,
the company has gone out of business.

00:31:15.999 --> 00:31:17.799
My father-in-law has let you all down.

00:31:18.400 --> 00:31:19.560
Let me apologize to you all

00:31:19.880 --> 00:31:21.559
on his behalf first.

00:31:21.559 --> 00:31:23.440
What's the point of apologizing?

00:31:25.660 --> 00:31:27.120
Let's talk about something practical.

00:31:27.120 --> 00:31:28.799
Let's not argue for now.

00:31:28.920 --> 00:31:30.120
They invited us here

00:31:30.120 --> 00:31:31.519
to resolve the issue.

00:31:31.540 --> 00:31:33.719
Let's wait for them
to finish their words first, okay?

00:31:34.680 --> 00:31:35.880
Hurry up.

00:31:35.880 --> 00:31:37.120
I'll see what you can tell me.

00:31:37.440 --> 00:31:38.239
Hurry up.

00:31:38.920 --> 00:31:40.120
We only found out about

00:31:40.120 --> 00:31:41.680
the company's situation not long ago.

00:31:42.319 --> 00:31:44.440
We weren't prepared for it at all.

00:31:44.719 --> 00:31:46.960
There's no money in
the company's bank account.

00:31:47.039 --> 00:31:50.239
However, we will work with the bank
and the company's finance department

00:31:50.239 --> 00:31:52.239
to develop a repayment plan for everyone.

00:31:53.279 --> 00:31:54.160
Please don't worry.

00:31:55.160 --> 00:31:57.479
We may go bankrupt
or beg for food on the streets,

00:31:58.160 --> 00:32:00.200
but we would never default on our debt.

00:32:01.440 --> 00:32:03.319
My dada cared about his reputation.

00:32:04.319 --> 00:32:05.440
Although he's gone,

00:32:05.440 --> 00:32:06.640
I, Feng Meiqi,

00:32:07.200 --> 00:32:08.239
won't let anything

00:32:08.239 --> 00:32:09.239
harm his reputation.

00:32:09.850 --> 00:32:11.160
Let's forget about that for now.

00:32:11.160 --> 00:32:12.519
It's not about his reputation here.

00:32:13.120 --> 00:32:14.999
Misters and madams,

00:32:15.200 --> 00:32:17.559
I understand your feelings completely.

00:32:18.880 --> 00:32:20.600
(Audit Report of Nanzhou Jianmei Workshop)
If we look at this audit report,

00:32:21.039 --> 00:32:22.519
legally speaking,

00:32:22.519 --> 00:32:24.479
we may choose not to repay the debt.

00:32:25.120 --> 00:32:26.999
But we invited all of you here

00:32:26.999 --> 00:32:28.519
in order to show you our determination.

00:32:28.920 --> 00:32:31.120
We'll definitely repay the debt.

00:32:31.559 --> 00:32:33.160
But please give us some time,

00:32:33.160 --> 00:32:33.680
okay?

00:32:33.680 --> 00:32:35.200
We've been paying for it
for a long time.

00:32:35.200 --> 00:32:36.600
We have to survive too.

00:32:36.610 --> 00:32:37.719
Things are difficult for us too.

00:32:37.719 --> 00:32:39.200
Come, dear debtors.

00:32:39.400 --> 00:32:41.279
Fellow debtors, listen to me.

00:32:41.280 --> 00:32:43.280
We live in a society
governed by the rule of law.

00:32:43.559 --> 00:32:45.160
Don't you think this farce is pointless?

00:32:45.920 --> 00:32:47.600
It doesn't resolve the issue at all.

00:32:49.279 --> 00:32:51.640
Just now, Feng's daughter
and daughter-in-law

00:32:51.999 --> 00:32:53.510
have already explained the situation.

00:32:55.110 --> 00:32:56.479
Don't you guys know who Feng is?

00:32:56.970 --> 00:32:59.260
We've been doing business
with him for several decades.

00:32:59.440 --> 00:33:01.600
He was serious and particular.

00:33:02.120 --> 00:33:03.759
I think his daughter and daughter-in-law

00:33:04.160 --> 00:33:05.799
handle things much more skillfully.

00:33:06.880 --> 00:33:07.559
Today,

00:33:07.920 --> 00:33:08.960
I'll express my stand.

00:33:10.759 --> 00:33:13.279
I choose to trust them

00:33:13.600 --> 00:33:14.799
and the Feng family.

00:33:16.460 --> 00:33:17.650
I'll wait for their repayment.

00:33:18.360 --> 00:33:18.960
Wang!

00:33:19.210 --> 00:33:20.160
Wang, what do you mean by that?

00:33:20.160 --> 00:33:21.200
What was that?

00:33:21.200 --> 00:33:21.600
Hey.

00:33:21.840 --> 00:33:23.120
We'll come up with a solution.

00:33:23.559 --> 00:33:24.559
Please give us some time.

00:33:24.559 --> 00:33:26.160
Fine. I'll trust you guys as well.

00:33:26.239 --> 00:33:27.479
But please hurry up.

00:33:27.479 --> 00:33:28.160
I've been waiting the whole week!

00:33:28.160 --> 00:33:29.279
Me too!

00:33:29.360 --> 00:33:30.160
Stop delaying it!

00:33:30.160 --> 00:33:30.999
Fine. I'll trust you one last time.

00:33:30.999 --> 00:33:32.559
I'll trust you guys one last time.

00:33:32.559 --> 00:33:33.360
This is the last time.

00:33:33.360 --> 00:33:33.960
Let's go.

00:33:33.960 --> 00:33:34.960
You'd better hurry up.

00:33:35.799 --> 00:33:36.600
Stop crying.

00:33:36.600 --> 00:33:37.319
I'll trust you guys.

00:33:37.319 --> 00:33:38.160
We expect good news from you.

00:33:38.160 --> 00:33:38.920
- Wang!
- Okay.

00:33:39.880 --> 00:33:40.920
Let's go.

00:33:52.460 --> 00:33:53.840
We'll get through this eventually.

00:33:54.640 --> 00:33:55.479
Thank you, Mingzhu.

00:33:59.039 --> 00:34:00.680
Mr. Zhang, I'm truly sorry.

00:34:00.680 --> 00:34:01.840
(This account is banned)
Our account

00:34:01.864 --> 00:34:02.999
(The content cannot be viewed)
was banned for no reason.

00:34:02.999 --> 00:34:04.319
We've already submitted an appeal.

00:34:05.200 --> 00:34:07.550
Can you hold off on
releasing that ad for a few more days?

00:34:07.680 --> 00:34:08.440
What about this?

00:34:08.440 --> 00:34:10.999
I'll write three more articles for you.

00:34:11.199 --> 00:34:12.199
They're free.

00:34:12.639 --> 00:34:13.880
Today is our store anniversary.

00:34:14.170 --> 00:34:15.960
The ads will be pointless
if we delay it now.

00:34:16.040 --> 00:34:17.679
Forget it. Let's terminate the contract.

00:34:18.119 --> 00:34:19.770
I won't pursue
any legal responsibilities.

00:34:20.320 --> 00:34:20.960
Okay.

00:34:21.120 --> 00:34:22.440
Thank you for your understanding.

00:34:22.760 --> 00:34:24.800
I will refund
the full payment to you, then.

00:34:25.800 --> 00:34:26.479
Goodbye.

00:34:26.679 --> 00:34:27.920
I'm truly sorry about this.

00:34:38.440 --> 00:34:39.709
(Piano Teacher Ms. Huang)
Mrs. Zhang,

00:34:39.733 --> 00:34:41.280
the piano lessons need to be renewed.

00:34:41.360 --> 00:34:42.420
The total is 22,000 yuan.

00:34:52.780 --> 00:34:54.140
(Superior)

00:34:56.440 --> 00:34:57.559
My superior is calling me.

00:34:57.560 --> 00:34:58.800
Shouldn't you go somewhere else?

00:34:59.519 --> 00:35:00.679
Go ahead.

00:35:03.159 --> 00:35:03.800
Yes, ma'am.

00:35:04.240 --> 00:35:05.079
What's your order?

00:35:05.479 --> 00:35:07.199
The piano lessons need to be renewed.

00:35:08.280 --> 00:35:09.920
What? Again?

00:35:10.160 --> 00:35:11.679
Didn't I just pay for it not long ago?

00:35:11.960 --> 00:35:12.599
Buddy,

00:35:12.999 --> 00:35:14.920
time flies, you know?

00:35:15.159 --> 00:35:16.639
It's already been a year since then.

00:35:19.440 --> 00:35:20.639
I heard this about

00:35:21.280 --> 00:35:23.320
the son of Li De, my colleague.

00:35:24.119 --> 00:35:25.320
He merely took online lessons.

00:35:25.800 --> 00:35:27.720
Even so, he passed Grade 10.

00:35:27.730 --> 00:35:29.320
Hey, some people
don't even need lessons.

00:35:29.320 --> 00:35:30.720
Some of them can't even read scores.

00:35:30.999 --> 00:35:31.679
Zhang Hao,

00:35:31.920 --> 00:35:34.159
can we set higher standards
for ourselves?

00:35:34.320 --> 00:35:35.760
Piano is the king of all instruments.

00:35:35.770 --> 00:35:37.920
If we want our child to learn piano,
we should be serious.

00:35:37.920 --> 00:35:39.559
We have to see it through.

00:35:40.079 --> 00:35:41.479
I know that.

00:35:41.479 --> 00:35:43.060
It's not like I'm canceling the lesson.

00:35:45.599 --> 00:35:47.479
Isn't my payroll card with you?

00:35:47.479 --> 00:35:49.039
Isn't your bonus card with you?

00:35:50.460 --> 00:35:53.790
Zhang Hao, don't tell me you suck so much
that you're not getting a bonus this year.

00:35:53.800 --> 00:35:54.999
That's impossible.

00:35:55.320 --> 00:35:56.720
I'm not that terrible at my job.

00:35:57.460 --> 00:35:58.559
Hey, about your selection...

00:35:58.559 --> 00:35:59.320
Coming!

00:36:00.440 --> 00:36:01.679
They're calling me to work.

00:36:01.720 --> 00:36:03.240
I'm busy. Talk to you later.

00:36:06.479 --> 00:36:09.440
He's a man, yet he can't afford
to raise a single child.

00:36:09.960 --> 00:36:11.199
And, how dare he...

00:36:23.720 --> 00:36:24.360
Mom.

00:36:25.599 --> 00:36:27.479
Did you change the password at the door?

00:36:27.480 --> 00:36:29.150
Were you trying to prevent me
from coming in?

00:36:29.240 --> 00:36:30.550
Luckily, I didn't forget my keys.

00:36:30.720 --> 00:36:31.320
Granny.

00:36:32.039 --> 00:36:32.840
Come.

00:36:32.850 --> 00:36:34.920
I brought some meat buns
from the company's canteen.

00:36:34.920 --> 00:36:35.960
They're very delicious.

00:36:36.079 --> 00:36:38.079
I love those meat buns.

00:36:39.320 --> 00:36:40.519
Are you in trouble?

00:36:42.519 --> 00:36:44.240
Don't beat around the bush.

00:36:47.080 --> 00:36:48.159
Get straight to the point.

00:36:48.240 --> 00:36:49.039
I lack money.

00:36:50.559 --> 00:36:52.280
We need to renew Jiao's piano lessons.

00:36:52.800 --> 00:36:54.840
And, Zhixia's official account
is still banned.

00:36:54.920 --> 00:36:56.079
She's very anxious.

00:36:56.079 --> 00:36:57.440
She wants me to pay half of it.

00:36:57.440 --> 00:36:58.240
I'm a little...

00:36:58.800 --> 00:37:00.320
What? You can't even afford that?

00:37:00.320 --> 00:37:03.240
Why would I come here with meat buns
if I could afford it in the first place?

00:37:03.240 --> 00:37:05.039
So, you came here
with an ulterior motive,

00:37:05.560 --> 00:37:06.999
thinking that I would help you out?

00:37:07.479 --> 00:37:08.240
Correct.

00:37:08.999 --> 00:37:11.440
It's a shame that Mom isn't a cop
when she's this observant.

00:37:11.440 --> 00:37:12.880
She's good at discovering issues.

00:37:13.440 --> 00:37:15.039
We can pay for it.

00:37:15.920 --> 00:37:16.840
We save up money

00:37:17.079 --> 00:37:18.559
for Jiao's sake anyway.

00:37:19.159 --> 00:37:19.840
Am I right?

00:37:22.760 --> 00:37:23.660
How much do you need?

00:37:23.920 --> 00:37:25.599
Transfer 10,000 yuan to me.

00:37:25.599 --> 00:37:26.519
I mean, 11,000 yuan.

00:37:26.840 --> 00:37:27.679
Don't worry.

00:37:27.690 --> 00:37:29.850
I'll return the money to you
right after I receive my bonus.

00:37:30.280 --> 00:37:32.280
With that measly bonus of yours? Geez.

00:37:32.280 --> 00:37:33.720
What did you say? Granny, look at Mom.

00:37:33.720 --> 00:37:34.920
Of all the things to say.

00:37:35.320 --> 00:37:36.880
Enough. Transfer extra money to him.

00:37:36.880 --> 00:37:38.920
Youngsters like them
have plenty of expenses.

00:37:38.920 --> 00:37:40.480
And, they're under huge pressure too.

00:37:43.039 --> 00:37:44.250
Zhang Hao, let me ask you this.

00:37:44.479 --> 00:37:47.599
Zhixia wouldn't use the money you
transfer to her to support her family, right?

00:37:47.599 --> 00:37:48.720
How could that be?

00:37:49.440 --> 00:37:50.920
This money

00:37:50.920 --> 00:37:51.960
is only meant for Jiao.

00:37:52.079 --> 00:37:53.079
It's only meant for her.

00:37:54.920 --> 00:37:55.519
Transfer it.

00:37:55.999 --> 00:37:56.599
Fine.

00:38:01.599 --> 00:38:02.400
Did you receive it?

00:38:05.599 --> 00:38:06.280
Yeah.

00:38:06.559 --> 00:38:09.199
Look. It's only meant for
Jiao's piano lessons.

00:38:09.519 --> 00:38:11.240
Mom is particular indeed.

00:38:11.760 --> 00:38:12.880
Thank you, Mom.

00:38:14.720 --> 00:38:15.599
Have some meat buns.

00:38:15.599 --> 00:38:16.519
- Come on.
- They're delicious.

00:38:16.519 --> 00:38:18.079
No way. They're so expensive.

00:38:21.199 --> 00:38:21.999
Yeah. You should eat up.

00:38:21.999 --> 00:38:22.960
These meat buns cost over 10,000 yuan.

00:38:22.960 --> 00:38:23.479
Yeah.

00:38:25.060 --> 00:38:26.850
I'll have some tangerines.
You can have these.

00:38:28.880 --> 00:38:29.479
Mister.

00:38:29.999 --> 00:38:30.519
Hello.

00:38:31.960 --> 00:38:33.720
What's the gold price for today?

00:38:35.519 --> 00:38:37.840
It has risen a bit.

00:38:37.999 --> 00:38:38.950
The rate is pretty good.

00:38:41.039 --> 00:38:41.960
What do you need?

00:38:44.479 --> 00:38:46.320
I wish to sell these two gold bars.

00:38:48.400 --> 00:38:49.340
You wish to sell them?

00:38:51.079 --> 00:38:51.800
Okay.

00:38:52.599 --> 00:38:53.800
Let me weigh them first.

00:38:53.999 --> 00:38:54.559
Okay.

00:39:01.199 --> 00:39:02.199
Please take a look.

00:39:02.199 --> 00:39:03.519
It's precisely 40 gram.

00:39:03.519 --> 00:39:04.639
Please wait here.

00:39:04.639 --> 00:39:06.039
I'll go and test them first.

00:39:15.920 --> 00:39:17.360
(The company is insolvent.)

00:39:17.640 --> 00:39:18.999
(Their house has been mortgaged.)

00:39:19.639 --> 00:39:21.800
(The monthly interest
already amounts to 10,000 yuan.)

00:39:22.400 --> 00:39:24.070
(And, it has been
overdue for two months.)

00:39:24.599 --> 00:39:27.280
(By selling these gold bars,
I can settle the interest for now.)

00:39:27.960 --> 00:39:30.400
(But what about next month
or the month after that?)

00:39:30.880 --> 00:39:31.679
All done.

00:39:32.079 --> 00:39:32.880
There's no problem.

00:39:33.119 --> 00:39:33.679
Okay.

00:39:33.680 --> 00:39:35.639
Should I transfer the money
to your Alipay account?

00:39:35.639 --> 00:39:36.639
Or your WeChat account?

00:39:37.800 --> 00:39:39.400
Please transfer it to this card.

00:39:40.140 --> 00:39:42.980
Like the quiet pull of longing

00:39:45.380 --> 00:39:47.420
As seasons pass me by

00:39:47.420 --> 00:39:50.280
And time keeps softly ticking on

00:39:50.280 --> 00:39:51.360
I can't afford to sell these.

00:39:51.360 --> 00:39:52.660
Maybe I've come to understand a little

00:39:52.660 --> 00:39:54.340
And learned to finally
let some things go

00:39:54.340 --> 00:39:58.740
All the bittersweet years
are youth itself

00:39:58.740 --> 00:40:02.620
Life gives us sunshine

00:40:02.620 --> 00:40:06.220
Never forgets to strike

00:40:06.220 --> 00:40:10.300
Some say you just have
to swallow the pain

00:40:10.300 --> 00:40:13.900
Yet fleeting clouds can't compare
to flowers blooming in the wind

00:40:13.900 --> 00:40:17.660
I write a long letter of my heart

00:40:17.660 --> 00:40:21.300
Letting love unfold softly across time

00:40:21.300 --> 00:40:25.300
To every turn that fate has drawn

00:40:28.639 --> 00:40:29.320
Mingzhu.

00:40:29.320 --> 00:40:29.840
Mom.

00:40:33.079 --> 00:40:33.639
Here.

00:40:34.360 --> 00:40:36.079
I made you chicken soup with noodles.

00:40:36.080 --> 00:40:37.940
I've rinsed
the preserved vegetables in water.

00:40:37.960 --> 00:40:39.550
I've mixed it with
some sesame oil as well.

00:40:39.760 --> 00:40:40.880
It's no longer salty.

00:40:41.479 --> 00:40:42.479
I'm not hungry.

00:40:43.840 --> 00:40:44.760
Just take a bite.

00:40:46.400 --> 00:40:46.960
Okay.

00:40:58.599 --> 00:40:59.240
Mingzhu.

00:41:00.760 --> 00:41:04.079
Regarding the debt
Jianqi's dad has incurred,

00:41:04.430 --> 00:41:05.999
how do you guys intend to deal with it?

00:41:06.880 --> 00:41:08.760
We'll deal with it as we're supposed to.

00:41:09.559 --> 00:41:11.119
We have already clarified our assets

00:41:11.199 --> 00:41:13.060
and are reconciling accounts
with our debtors.

00:41:14.680 --> 00:41:16.559
Mingzhu, I think
you should let Jianqi's sister

00:41:16.559 --> 00:41:18.720
handle these affairs.

00:41:19.360 --> 00:41:20.599
Look at you.

00:41:21.360 --> 00:41:22.360
You're still pregnant.

00:41:22.599 --> 00:41:24.079
You shouldn't be stressed out.

00:41:24.360 --> 00:41:26.760
You shouldn't get involved in this mess.

00:41:27.039 --> 00:41:27.880
I have to.

00:41:28.800 --> 00:41:30.800
He already transferred
the house ownership to me.

00:41:31.240 --> 00:41:32.720
I can't just go into hiding

00:41:32.720 --> 00:41:33.800
when they're in trouble.

00:41:34.039 --> 00:41:34.639
Am I right?

00:41:37.119 --> 00:41:38.559
It's fine. I can do this.

00:41:42.360 --> 00:41:43.999
Eat slowly.

00:41:44.679 --> 00:41:46.999
Why don't you spend the night here?

00:41:46.999 --> 00:41:48.800
I have to go back tonight.

00:41:48.880 --> 00:41:50.880
Alright.
I'll ask Minghui to send you home.

00:41:51.360 --> 00:41:51.880
Okay.

00:41:51.960 --> 00:41:52.479
Yeah.

00:41:52.800 --> 00:41:54.320
Eat slowly. There's no rush.

00:41:57.440 --> 00:41:58.079
Minghui.

00:41:58.560 --> 00:41:59.639
What's the matter, Mingzhu?

00:42:00.599 --> 00:42:03.800
Don't you think
my life has been pretty tough?

00:42:04.960 --> 00:42:05.800
I lost my husband,

00:42:06.290 --> 00:42:07.680
and I've lost all of our wealth too.

00:42:08.160 --> 00:42:09.559
Mingzhu, the wealth is still there.

00:42:10.599 --> 00:42:11.920
It's just that it's negative now.

00:42:13.519 --> 00:42:14.320
Isn't my life bitter?

00:42:15.240 --> 00:42:16.320
Isn't your life bitter?

00:42:16.330 --> 00:42:18.950
Is anything more bitter than
being in the fifth year of high school?

00:42:24.920 --> 00:42:26.360
Mingzhu, open your mouth.

00:42:29.639 --> 00:42:30.800
It's not as bitter now, right?

00:42:34.159 --> 00:42:34.760
It's sweet.

00:42:35.639 --> 00:42:36.880
No matter what happens,

00:42:37.479 --> 00:42:39.679
I'll always stand by you.

00:42:55.100 --> 00:42:56.950
The world is noisy

00:42:57.550 --> 00:42:59.930
Turning around,
it's already a distant view

00:43:01.350 --> 00:43:03.230
Once I didnt know what to do

00:43:03.230 --> 00:43:05.310
What to hold quietly

00:43:05.310 --> 00:43:08.260
Like a silent care

00:43:10.120 --> 00:43:12.530
Seasons pass by

00:43:12.530 --> 00:43:15.390
Time ticks away

00:43:15.880 --> 00:43:17.790
Seems like I understand a little

00:43:17.790 --> 00:43:19.570
And also let go of some things

00:43:19.570 --> 00:43:24.290
All the bittersweet flavors
are the essence of youth

00:43:24.290 --> 00:43:27.780
A long letter is written down

00:43:27.930 --> 00:43:31.410
Gently spreading love

00:43:31.610 --> 00:43:35.600
To all the forks in fate

00:43:35.600 --> 00:43:41.230
Loving all the moments
that deserve to be loved